              }
}
Node "Ferd_2_2a_3b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Although not as bad as America, Mexico was hit pretty bad, you know? All the cities are in ruins. Perhaps the radiation is not so bad as it is around here, though."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why do you think Mexico was attacked during the war?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Which part of Mexico do you come from?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why don't you return to Mexico?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3c_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. Please tell me what you do, here." linkto "Ferd_3_1b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to be going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Ferd_2_2a_3b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[Ferdinand grins.] That come to be something of a joke in Mexico. Amongst the survivors, at least."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- MORE -" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3b_3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Ferd_2_2a_3b_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Some, they say the Reds see Mexico as a big friend and ally of America, so they blow us up. Others, they say America was not so keen on Mexico surviving the war so close to them and perhaps taking over, so the gringos take us with them."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Which of the two do you think is true?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3b_4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Which part of Mexico do you come from?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why don't you return to Mexico?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3c_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. Please tell me what you do, here." linkto "Ferd_3_1b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to be going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Ferd_2_2a_3b_4"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[He shrugs.] I don' really give it much thought. I don' see what difference it make."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Which part of Mexico do you come from?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why don't you return to Mexico?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3c_1"  notes ""
