Node "Ferd_2_2a_3c_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Maybe when I was a younger man I would have returned if had made enough money. I am too old now, though. Mexico, she has probably changed too much since I left."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How long has it been since you left Mexico?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3c_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Which part of Mexico do you come from?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How badly was Mexico damaged during the war?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. Please tell me what you do, here." linkto "Ferd_3_1b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to be going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Ferd_2_2a_3c_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Ay, you're asking me a tough question, there. I don' know, say maybe twenty-five or thirty years ago? It seem like a lifetime ago."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Which part of Mexico do you come from?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How badly was Mexico damaged during the war?" linkto "Ferd_2_2a_3b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. Please tell me what you do, here." linkto "Ferd_3_1b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to be going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Ferd_2_2b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[He laughs.] Tha's pretty funny! No, amigo, before the war, Mexico used to be a country, like America."
 NPCFemaleText "[He laughs.] Tha's pretty funny! No, Seńorita, before the war, Mexico used to be a country, like America."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How could I find it?" linkto "Ferd_2_2b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. Please tell me what you are doing here." linkto "Ferd_3_1b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Don't laugh at me. You're the one who talks like an idiot." linkto "Ferd_1a_2b_2B_2b_1"  notes "If the variable Ferd_Rude>3 then enter combat instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I must leave." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
